    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/c598f3-79/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=610161848511103782&sectionId=610166881323582246)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnBm-lLAI9_text","label":"ggnBm-lLAI9_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#4C4E57;\">Why People</span> <span style=\"color:#B76C45;\">Trust Reviv</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGJtDiLSQD_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggGJtDiLSQD_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Abdullah_Khalid.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrutWAgWnW_text","label":"ggrutWAgWnW_text","default":"<p>They mocked it. Scoffed at it. REVIV? Just another gimmick. The nights I couldn’t sleep, jaw clenched from the weight of it all. But REVIV was different. It didn’t just straighten my smile, It rebuilt my discipline. You either chew through the pain… Or you stay stuck in it. I chose REVIV.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3kuAogyUj_text","label":"gg3kuAogyUj_text","default":"<p>— Abdullah</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbsF7Ch6Rf_text","label":"ggbsF7Ch6Rf_text","default":"<p>Verified Customer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYNu0V9CMt_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggYNu0V9CMt_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Jason_P.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gga_NSS4RQL_text","label":"gga_NSS4RQL_text","default":"<p>I’ve tried two different night guards from my dentist and they helped protect my teeth, but I was still clenching all night. With Reviv I became aware of the clenching almost immediately. It feels different. My jaw doesn’t lock down the same way. I still catch myself clenching sometimes, but it’s not constant like before.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAGsvPh_74_text","label":"ggAGsvPh_74_text","default":"<p>— Jason</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3mRmDF-MX_text","label":"gg3mRmDF-MX_text","default":"<p>Verified Customer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggumS_She0t_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggumS_She0t_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Tiara_C.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjR-VGzu0D_text","label":"ggjR-VGzu0D_text","default":"<p>I wore a custom night guard for years. It stopped the damage, but it never stopped the clenching. It didn’t feel like I was just blocking the grind. It felt like my jaw wasn’t fighting itself anymore. It’s not magic, but it’s the first time I’ve felt actual relief instead of just protection.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWN_i4ecxq_text","label":"ggWN_i4ecxq_text","default":"<p>— Tiara</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3lvMqexiU_text","label":"gg3lvMqexiU_text","default":"<p>Verified Customer</p>"}],
